task.summary: Migrated project to Maven. This includes: 1) A semi-functioning build process, IntelliJ form files are not compatible with Maven. That's why I made them generate source code instead of xml to help alleviate this problem. So far most of the elements are loaded properly aside from the lectures in the joinableLectures table. 2) Fixed package declarations
Updated SQLite version and commented out several plugins that are not used in the current generation of the jar file (maven stuff)
Commiting workspace.xml to fix merging issue.
Added lecture details for each selected lecture and moved the code from LectureDetailsView to a Intellij form.
Fixed a bug where the selected row from the right table was not properly updated.
Added missing icon.png and fixed the filepath for the image.
